                <div style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700;">Barrister Raza Khan Niazi</div>
                <div style="font-size: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 2px; font-weight: bold;">Digital Seal Verification</div>
